OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud and fog dissipating
OL,6,Finland resulting in warm afternoon
OL,7,Fsunshine. Cloud lingering along the
OL,8,Fcoast with a moderate easterly breeze
OL,9,Fresulting in a cooler feel.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLow cloud along the coast,
OL,12,Fwill spread westwards with patchy rain
OL,13,Fand hill fog possible, driven by
OL,14,Fbreezy easterly winds. Staying mild
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy periods throughout
OL,18,FSunday, though brighter in the
OL,19,Fafternoon especially in the south of
OL,20,Fthe region. Temperatures inland stay
OL,21,Fwarm but cooler along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
