OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fand largely sunny conditions on Monday
OL,7,Fwith coastal cloud. Some patchy cloud
OL,8,FTuesday morning, brightening up later.
OL,9,FFoggy and cloudy start to Wednesday
OL,10,Fwith afternoon sunshine. Temperatures
OL,11,Faround average.
